LIMIT 50;

LIMIT 50

LIMIT 50;

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE t.trade.name == '金融服务' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') RETURN t.trade.name, td.trade_data.`date`, td.trade_data.minimum_price, td.trade_data.opening_price, td.trade_data.`date`, td.trade_data.closing_price
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE ( t.trade.name == "金融" OR t.trade.name == "服务" ) AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN td.trade_data.`date`,td.trade_data.closing_price,td.trade_data.minimum_price
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( t.trade.name == "金融" OR t.trade.name == "服务" ) 
RETURN td.trade_data.`date`,td.trade_data.closing_price,td.trade_data.minimum_price
LIMIT 50
